IMAPStore posteo-remote
Host posteo.de
Port 993
User abbreviatedman@posteo.net
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty --decrypt ~/.password-store/mail/posteo/abbreviatedman.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore posteo-local
Path ~/.local/mail/posteo/abbreviatedman/
Inbox ~/.local/mail/posteo/abbreviatedman/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel posteo
Far :posteo-remote:
Near :posteo-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *
